{
  "page": "Bold Marilda",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Bold Marilda</b></i> was a war galley in service to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Velaryon\" title=\"House Velaryon\">House Velaryon</a>. It was <a href=\"/index.php/Named_after\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Named after\">named after</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Marilda_of_Hull\" title=\"Marilda of Hull\">Marilda of Hull</a>, the mother of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyn Velaryon\">Alyn Velaryon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bold_Marilda&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyn Velaryon\">Alyn Velaryon</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Tides\" title=\"Lord of the Tides\">Lord of the Tides</a>, sailed on <i>Bold Marilda</i> when he led a fleet of <a href=\"/index.php?title=Merchantman&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Merchantman (page does not exist)\">merchantmen</a> and a dozen war <a href=\"/index.php/Galley\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Galley\">galleys</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/136_AC\" title=\"136 AC\">136&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bold_Marilda&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Lysene Spring and the End of Regency.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405011526\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.020 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.042 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 221/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8607/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 818/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 418/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1077/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.5 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   37.168      1 -total\n 77.99%   28.987      1 Template:Date\n 16.80%    6.245      2 Template:Ref\n 10.64%    3.956      2 Template:Ref/core\n  4